Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.99,0:00:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕上了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.48,0:00:10.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有打電話回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.50,0:00:13.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是趕上集合時間了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:16.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經到車站了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.42,0:00:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有忘帶東西就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.48,0:00:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛這樣想的時候一看房間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.41,0:00:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個忘帶的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.04,0:00:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓澪學姐她們替你多拍點好照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.34,0:00:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走好  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.22,0:02:09.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「現在在富士山裡  能看到新幹線」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.57,0:02:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐好像很開心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:15.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:19.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  就因為憂這樣  唯學姐才一直無法自立
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  無法自立？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.41,0:02:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經高三了  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.53,0:02:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在活動室裡也一直是懶懶散散地盡吃零食
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.06,0:02:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不生氣的話就不會練習
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:34.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小梓認為姐姐變得很嚴格比較好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:40.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了  唯學姐如果能認真幹的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中野  你和大家沒有合拍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.49,0:02:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:51.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在看什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.62,0:02:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是姐姐發來的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.83,0:03:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憂的姐姐真有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.22,0:03:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛也收到了爵士研的學長發來的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:10.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「一年生就拜託你了」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很認真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.69,0:03:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是唯學姐發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.73,0:03:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…「小豬的飼料就拜託了」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.42,0:03:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真丟臉…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:26.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成輕音社是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:30.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天來踢易開罐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:38.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒糟糕到那種地步呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.98,0:03:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  夢幻的黃金巧克力麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.82,0:03:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩年來第一次見到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一天只有三個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:56.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像總是高三的先買掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小純  來拍張紀念照吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.53,0:04:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小純  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  姐姐發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.13,0:04:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.11,0:04:19.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說便當盒忘在教室裡了  讓我帶回家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.50,0:04:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我這樣子很難為情啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打攪了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:42.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以進去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是來拿忘記的東西嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.25,0:04:52.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…唯學姐的座位我記得是在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶  澪學姐的座位呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:04.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得應該是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  感覺好像變酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.33,0:05:14.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.27,0:05:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抽？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.08,0:05:20.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不行啊  隨便…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…這是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律學姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  憂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是姐姐的桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.06,0:05:33.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這麼喜歡姐姐的話不會感到寂寞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.49,0:05:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.61,0:05:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要到後天才回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊…姐姐不回來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才意識到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起  今天我們會去你家玩的  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至住在你家也行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是…她們今天會住在我家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為回禮  要去幫忙爵士研的練習
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樂器數量的話  連吹奏樂團都比不上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:13.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這麼多彈的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:14.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  真厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  爵士研是生存戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.96,0:06:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要在學長們不在時候努力練習…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.14,0:06:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  貝斯忘在教室裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.54,0:06:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子啊  純
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我們是小純的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你是梓學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:47.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純學姐說的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:52.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「輕音社裡有個吉他彈得很好的學姐  讓她教你們」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.09,0:06:57.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.61,0:07:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.96,0:07:03.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.88,0:07:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們兩個是我們的一年生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓  你教教她們吉他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:16.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2  3  4
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2  3  4
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:21.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那段很難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手指無法很好地活動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:27.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就來做一下手指的柔軟體操吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣把按弦的手的手指併攏後伸出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.17,0:07:38.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食指和中指分開  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把無名指和小拇指分開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2  3  4
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:48.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1  2  3  4
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:50.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手指抽痙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.01,0:07:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.27,0:07:55.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  憂能做到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:59.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因為陪姐姐做過柔軟體操
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在洗澡的時候或是演奏之前做的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.94,0:08:06.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手指就會漸漸得變靈活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.05,0:08:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小純？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.21,0:08:15.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼辦  手指動不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷…冷場了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:34.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一些微薄小禮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:39.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還請笑納
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.18,0:08:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.46,0:08:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜甜圈？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:47.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  Super all star bag
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.78,0:08:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都想買一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:53.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:09:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是三個人  所以稍微多做了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  如果不夠的話  還有散壽司和披薩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.93,0:09:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了  已經很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:13.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.06,0:09:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.49,0:09:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…這是媽媽讓我帶來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡…裡面是什麼  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？  是壽司
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.49,0:09:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜甜圈吃不下了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.64,0:09:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.88,0:09:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經吃不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.15,0:09:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我想試下味道嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓  剩下的你都可以吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能吃得下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜食是吃不飽的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.21,0:09:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力什麼的很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.86,0:10:06.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好甜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  姐姐發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.05,0:10:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺像修學旅行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「憂你們也在享受住宿的快樂嗎」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:24.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.51,0:10:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我滾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.26,0:10:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.75,0:10:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.96,0:10:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.71,0:10:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們也睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.54,0:10:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還不困
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們在被子裡聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.26,0:10:50.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關燈咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯學姐她們現在一定很開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.57,0:11:00.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定已經睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:01.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合宿的時候大家也玩到很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:06.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.24,0:11:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特產？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我們玩得太開心就給忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.47,0:11:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來喝茶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.35,0:11:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得還不至於變成那樣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.71,0:11:28.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～真好啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  明天去哪裡玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:34.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:36.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼想去的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個  
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.25,0:11:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去動物園…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我也想去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.13,0:11:46.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:47.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.40,0:11:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.07,0:11:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐發來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骷髏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:05.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.27,0:12:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,K-ON!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:18.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.79,0:12:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.61,0:12:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:33.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有新的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不…要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:56.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓  會不會綁得太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:13:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓的頭髮真好  又黑又直
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.49,0:13:06.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  經常被說像日本人偶一樣  其實蠻討厭的說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:10.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是蠻好的嘛  我每天打理很麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別像今天這樣的雨天…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.78,0:13:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  好卷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今…今天戴個帽子怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:22.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.46,0:13:28.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傾盆大雨啊  
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  看樣子沒法去動物園了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～  好想去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:39.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純  有什麼好玩的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有想去的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:43.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.22,0:13:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲什麼的也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.65,0:13:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憂  這個有第六卷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.25,0:13:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  這可不好說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:59.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到朋友家這麼做  我覺得會失去朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.35,0:14:03.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得應該是在姐姐的書架上…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是你姐姐的房間？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.51,0:14:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這是之前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.19,0:14:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  前段時間搬了一堆回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大掃除時候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:16.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.68,0:14:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是吉太啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.89,0:14:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  好帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…啊  有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  第七卷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我想看第六卷啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:30.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.85,0:14:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只有第七卷之後的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少看一卷嘛  沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.64,0:14:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就…看看吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…果然不行  去書店吧  去書店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:44.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:46.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面還下著大雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:52.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然覺得好無聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.54,0:14:55.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我剛才問有沒有什麼能玩的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.61,0:14:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是唯學姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:04.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「梓喵  你們在幹什麼？」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…果然還是去哪裡玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.46,0:15:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡得好快啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是打擊練習場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為看的是棒球漫畫嘛  就想來試試了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.97,0:15:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種球怎麼可能打中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到那邊抓娃娃去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:29.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄得好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憂怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…果然好難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.85,0:15:40.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看著球  等待其靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.55,0:15:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像這裡有一面牆  
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揮棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.75,0:15:54.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待其靠近  想像一面牆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.86,0:15:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揮棒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:57.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:15:58.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:15:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:01.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:04.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打中了啊  小梓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.01,0:16:05.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.24,0:16:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憂學東西真是快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:12.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點和唯學姐一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:13.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.86,0:16:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:18.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大  這就是全壘打獎品嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:19.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.87,0:16:25.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這麼大往哪裡放啊  都有小豬10倍…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把小豬給忘了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  還是那麼精神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.44,0:16:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起啊  小豬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.77,0:16:52.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子就是小豬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.78,0:16:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實蠻可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.13,0:16:57.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐經常在說「和梓喵一樣可愛」哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:11.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡啊  第六卷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.45,0:17:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來對了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  見到小豬確實是蠻好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這雨要下到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得的週日啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.87,0:17:32.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  三個人來場即興演出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:33.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.22,0:17:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨這麼大  聲音大點應該也沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.83,0:17:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:41.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:43.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這好像挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.99,0:17:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我能彈好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:49.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題  就玩點簡單的好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.43,0:17:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風琴應該能彈吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.57,0:17:54.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小時候我彈過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:57.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彈吧  彈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:17:58.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.22,0:18:02.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純  爵士研裡有吉他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊  等我一會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:17.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.65,0:18:22.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2 3 4 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:57.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.51,0:19:01.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊  感覺曲子很酷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.52,0:19:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:05.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨停了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.67,0:19:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:24.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是姐姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「嗚～好想吉太啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.64,0:19:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  梓再過去點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.58,0:19:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:40.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了嗎  要拍咯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.05,0:19:42.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.29,0:19:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發給姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天見了  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.82,0:19:55.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憂  第七卷拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.93,0:20:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看著看著坐過頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.77,0:20:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.88,0:20:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過玩得好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是唯學姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.60,0:20:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  梓喵？我們現在迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.05,0:20:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給梓打電話有什麼用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.76,0:20:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.15,0:20:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  姐姐說梓喵成分不足了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是該藏起來…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.03,0:20:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見不見了～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.47,0:20:55.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請住手啊  這是在走廊上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:57.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵果然好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:20:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:20:59.27,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都叫你住手了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.38,0:21:02.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  給你帶禮物了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.42,0:21:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都在活動室等著  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  過一會再去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.29,0:21:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  紬紬都把茶泡好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:16.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯…唯學姐  等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:19.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.36,0:21:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BU？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是禮物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.70,0:21:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  我是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.21,0:21:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預備～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.68,0:21:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.34,0:21:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「桶社員」！是指熱愛桶的社員！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.34,0:21:39.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（「おけ」除桶外也可以理解為管弦樂）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.46,0:21:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你胡扯的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.30,0:21:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IBUONKE！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.41,0:21:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棲息在東北地區的妖怪名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.39,0:21:45.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是胡扯！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.43,0:21:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  那我再來個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.37,0:21:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕音社
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.43,0:21:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:22:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…來練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～今天喝茶就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:05.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時差失調中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.04,0:22:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.60,0:23:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這說不定是什麼咒術
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.96,0:23:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.57,0:23:49.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨著誰  就對其下了詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.56,0:23:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.77,0:23:52.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.75,0:23:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.98,0:23:56.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平澤同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:23:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.74,0:24:01.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得的機會  想穿別的衣服看看
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.18,0:24:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.08,0:24:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你選這件！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.98,0:24:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明大家都很期待的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.05,0:24:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用回應大家的期待也可以


